form.congress: One Hundred Thirteenth Congress of the United States of America
form.enrolled-dateline: Begun and held at the City of Washington on Friday, the third day of January, two thousand and fourteen
form.official-title: Directing the Clerk of the House of Representatives to make technical corrections in the enrollment of H.R. 3370.

section.text: That, in the enrollment of the bill (H.R. 3370) to delay the implementation of certain provisions of the Biggert-Waters Flood Insurance Reform Act of 2012, and for other purposes, the Clerk of the House of Representatives shall make the following corrections:

subparagraph.text: in the matter preceding the new subsection added by the amendment made by such section, strike , as amended by the preceding provisions of this Act, is further and insert is; and
in the new subsection added by the amendment made by such section, strike (e) and insert (d).

paragraph.text: In section 14, before the closing quotation marks that immediately precede the period at the end insert and.

subparagraph.text: in the matter that precedes paragraph (1), strike is and insert the following: , as amended by section 27 of this Act, is further;

clause.text: in the matter that precedes subparagraph (A), strike subparagraph (B) and insert subparagraph (C); and

subclause.text: strike subparagraph (A) and insert subparagraph (B); and

subparagraph.text: in paragraph (2), strike and (C) as subparagraphs (D), (E), and (G) and insert (C), and (D) as subparagraphs (D), (E), (F), and (H);
in paragraph (3), in the matter preceding the new subparagraphs inserted by the amendment made by such paragraph, strike subparagraph (B) and insert subparagraph (D); and

clause.text: in the matter preceding the new subparagraph inserted by the amendment made by such paragraph, strike subparagraph (E) and insert subparagraph (F); and
in the new subparagraph inserted by the amendment made by such paragraph, strike (F) and insert (G).

attestation-group.role: Clerk of the House of Representatives.
